videos.description: Ole Miss receiver Elijah Moore says records are meant to be broken and QB Matt Corral credits the variety of athletes that make their offense special.
videos.headline: Connection between Corral and Moore is unmatched

videos.description: Ole Miss is back in the win column after record-setting days from QB Matt Corral (6 TDs) and WR Elijah Moore (238 yards) in a 54-21 victory over Vanderbilt.
videos.headline: Moore, Corral light up scoreboard to end losing streak
